The '''Kalphite Queen''' ('''''Kalphiscarabeinae pasha'''''<ref>Display case in [[Varrock Museum]] natural history exhibit, southern wing. "Kalphite Queen (Kalphiscarabeinae Pasha)"</ref>), also called the '''KQ''', is the strongest of the [[Kalphite (race)|Kalphites]].

She is a powerful opponent that makes use of [[protection prayers]], though they only function as an indicator to players of which attack styles may be most effective rather than outright blocking damage from them. She can use all three combat styles, of which her ranged and magic attacks always land as [[successful hit]]s, and has two forms.

Unique drops from the Queen include the [[dragon 2h sword]], [[dragon chainbody]], [[dragon pickaxe]] and [[kq head]] drops. Killing her is additionally a requirement for the [[Desert Diary]], with a hard task requiring players to kill her once and an elite task requiring the player to speak to a [[Kalphite Queen head (mounted)|mounted head]] inside their own [[Player-owned house]].

